BFN 

  [Text] Swaziland's Defense Force says it knows nothing 
about members of the Afrikaner Volksfront [National Front] 
apparently being trained in the north of the territory. This 
follows allegations by a Swazi chief that Volksfront members 
were receiving training in the area. The deputy commissioner of 
the Swazi police, Mr. Esau Dube, said that an investigation in 
this regard had proved fruitless. 

