<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The name of the Lebowan chief minister, Mr. Nelson 
Ramodike, has been taken off the ANC's national candidate list. 
The ANC office in Johannesburg has confirmed this, but declined 
to give any reason. Earlier Mr. Ramodike said he was unaware of 
